* The group meets Vorea, a scout who will lead them to the pass
* En route, Alatheia picks a flower and puts it in her braid, prays to Sune, thinking about the book
* Vorea goes a bit further ahead, and they arrive at the ridge.
* A few party members notice the raised platforms
* They attempt to sneak up but do a poor job, realize they've been noticed.
* Lenny chucks four of the giant recordings out as a distraction, and combat ensues
* They make pretty good work, but two archers try to escape
* Flicker chases and re-rages - the necrotic damage kills one, and the other surrenders
* They have a prisoner!
